    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 9 article about Peter Greenaway opera Writing to Vermeer, which misidentified singer Kathryn Harries and director Saskia Boddeke (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on July 9 about Peter Greenaway's opera ''Writing to Vermeer'' at Lincoln Center Festival 2000 misidentified the singer in the role of Maria Thins, Vermeer's mother-in-law. It is Kathryn Harries, not Susan Bickley. A music listing misidentified the director of the production. It is directed by Saskia Boddeke and Mr. Greenaway, not Robert Wilson.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
